{"tid":1463252,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪真係有蘋果日報報導嘅5000mW激光筆？","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:15:24.000Z","uid":1893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"22c49f54a6637a08ca6b6913bea79d2915759c7b","tid":1463252,"uid":1893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:32:04.000Z","msg":"15年蘋果日報報導過有5000mW嘅激光筆，講到好危險，照下就燶就盲<br />\n但其實係咪真係有咁高火數嘅激光筆呢？<br />\n上網見到有個表：<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">以下是常見的雷射用品功率:\n\n功率 用途\n1&ndash;5 mW 簡報用雷射筆\n5 mW CD-ROM\n5&ndash;10 mW DVD播放器 或 DVD-ROM drive\n100 mW 高速的CD-RW\n250 mW 16&times; DVD-R 燒寫\n400 mW DVD 24&times; 雙層記錄\n1 W 高功率雷射筆\n1&ndash;20 W 微細加工\n30&ndash;100 W 手術雷射器\n100&ndash;3000 W 工業雷射切割\n100 kW 軍事用</code></pre><br />\n5000mW去到微細加工㗎啦喎，可以上網買到咁容易？<br />\n我再搵下匪國嘅網購網站，標自己係5000mW嘅都係一百至百幾蚊，比例好唔合理喎......<br />\n<br />\n我講出嚟係想研究下，蘋果日報15年嘅報導究竟係咪準確？"},{"pid":"e7085c1ce8ddfb2a1efcbdae71f27049c429382e","tid":1463252,"uid":1893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02d4f7a4968c5ebcb1187366f42a2dadbfd1eb3","tid":1463252,"uid":1893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:02:55.000Z","msg":"網上有人話，好多標係5000mW都係吹大，實質得500"},{"pid":"afc216d3a861c35f734408917e13d3a75e38593e","tid":1463252,"uid":1893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:15:24.000Z","msg":"學術討論"}]}